7
00:00:43,740 --> 00:00:45,260
What took Ms. Wen so long?

8
00:00:45,260 --> 00:00:46,140
Are you an idiot?

9
00:00:46,150 --> 00:00:48,330
She went to the subway station
to pick up her boyfriend.

10
00:00:48,330 --> 00:00:49,790
Her boyfriend?

11
00:00:50,290 --> 00:00:51,620
He's either rich or powerful.

12
00:00:51,620 --> 00:00:52,770
Why would he take the subway?

13
00:00:53,080 --> 00:00:54,750
You're so ignorant.

14
00:00:55,110 --> 00:00:56,450
Zixuan's boyfriend

15
00:00:56,460 --> 00:00:58,080
is from a family of farmers.

16
00:00:58,240 --> 00:00:59,380
He's extremely poor.

17
00:00:59,880 --> 00:01:02,010
He helped her

18
00:01:02,010 --> 00:01:03,500
carry her luggage on the train,

19
00:01:03,500 --> 00:01:04,920
and Zixuan fell in love with him.

20
00:01:06,230 --> 00:01:08,020
Otherwise, why would a rich heiress

21
00:01:08,410 --> 00:01:09,840
choose a poor man?

22
00:01:10,340 --> 00:01:12,020
You don't know her at all.

23
00:01:12,300 --> 00:01:13,550
Zixuan was born

24
00:01:13,730 --> 00:01:15,660
to be a unique and reckless girl.

25
00:01:15,940 --> 00:01:17,100
However, I think this man

26
00:01:17,100 --> 00:01:18,340
is just her friend.

27
00:01:18,490 --> 00:01:19,800
She won't be happy with him.

28
00:01:19,800 --> 00:01:20,640
Exactly.

29
00:01:22,230 --> 00:01:23,070
By the way,

30
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:25,520
what did you prepare for her birthday?

31
00:01:25,730 --> 00:01:26,850
Speaking of which,

32
00:01:27,100 --> 00:01:29,150
I bought a 900-yuan scarf,

33
00:01:29,540 --> 00:01:31,180
but it turns out the other gifts

34
00:01:31,180 --> 00:01:32,660
are worth at least 1000 yuan.

35
00:01:33,380 --> 00:01:34,840
Mine must be the cheapest one.

36
00:01:35,220 --> 00:01:36,580
Don't worry.

37
00:01:36,580 --> 00:01:37,420
Zixuan

38
00:01:37,420 --> 00:01:39,340
doesn't care about the price.

39
00:01:39,340 --> 00:01:40,580
(Gift List)
She cares about

40
00:01:40,820 --> 00:01:41,860
the meaning

41
00:01:42,110 --> 00:01:43,180
behind it.

42
00:01:43,620 --> 00:01:46,020
(66 Yuan)

