00:02:15,300 --> 00:02:19,140
=Black&White Forest=

44
00:02:19,180 --> 00:02:22,140
=Episode 20=

45
00:02:28,180 --> 00:02:31,940
(Reception Room)

46
00:02:31,940 --> 00:02:32,980
(Binbin)

47
00:02:34,860 --> 00:02:35,700
(Binbin)

48
00:02:43,880 --> 00:02:45,780
You know what's going on with Bao.

49
00:02:46,180 --> 00:02:47,460
Just tell me the truth.

50
00:02:47,460 --> 00:02:48,720
Will he be alright?

51
00:02:51,180 --> 00:02:53,340
Don't make up a story.

52
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,440
I'm only in charge of business.

53
00:02:56,930 --> 00:02:57,920
I don't know about

54
00:02:58,860 --> 00:02:59,820
other things.

55
00:03:04,540 --> 00:03:06,980
(Reception Room)

56
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:16,900
(Reception Room)
Bin.

57
00:03:17,700 --> 00:03:18,760
Listen...

58
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:19,860
I don't understand.

59
00:03:20,460 --> 00:03:21,660
You arrested

60
00:03:21,660 --> 00:03:22,980
and then released him.

61
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,860
Now you're saying he hired a killer.

62
00:03:25,380 --> 00:03:26,260
Why did you let him go?

63
00:03:26,260 --> 00:03:27,480
Listen to me.

64
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:30,940
Look,

65
00:03:31,860 --> 00:03:33,140
it's not as simple as you think.

66
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:34,780
I'm thinking too simply?

67
00:03:34,780 --> 00:03:36,170
Then tell me how complicated it is.

68
00:03:36,410 --> 00:03:37,250
I...

69
00:03:40,860 --> 00:03:41,820
Let me ask you.

70
00:03:42,820 --> 00:03:44,220
Did you call Mr. Xing?

71
00:03:44,740 --> 00:03:45,980
Yes, but his phone is off.

72
00:03:46,500 --> 00:03:47,660
He's always doing this.

73
00:03:50,980 --> 00:03:51,820
What do you mean?

74
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:54,180
I've told you

75
00:03:55,140 --> 00:03:56,740
it's not that simple.

76
00:03:58,100 --> 00:03:59,380
Xing Liang is under interrogation,

77
00:03:59,380 --> 00:04:00,380
and Bao was arrested.

78
00:04:01,380 --> 00:04:03,100
How are these two things connected?

79
00:04:03,100 --> 00:04:05,740
Oh, no. How can they be related?

80
00:04:06,220 --> 00:04:08,140
Don't ask. It'll only make it worse.

81
00:04:11,370 --> 00:04:12,210
Thanks.

82
00:04:12,210 --> 00:04:14,130
The number you dialed is off...

83
00:04:15,290 --> 00:04:16,620
It's really off.

84
00:04:16,900 --> 00:04:17,740
Thanks.

85
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,440
Actually,

86
00:04:23,820 --> 00:04:25,340
from what I know about Bao,

87
00:04:25,740 --> 00:04:26,900
even if he's involved

88
00:04:26,900 --> 00:04:28,140
in the murder,

89
00:04:28,700 --> 00:04:30,580
he can't be a direct participant.

90
00:04:31,010 --> 00:04:31,870
Ms. Wen,

91
00:04:32,180 --> 00:04:33,340
don't worry.

92
00:04:37,410 --> 00:04:38,250
Binbin.

93
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:39,720
Binbin.

94
00:04:41,010 --> 00:04:41,850
Sister.

95
00:04:42,310 --> 00:04:43,370
Did you call him?

96
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:46,800
He didn't answer.

97
00:04:48,580 --> 00:04:50,020
What's going on?

98
00:04:50,020 --> 00:04:51,340
They don't know.

99
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:52,850
They took Bao back

100
00:04:53,080 --> 00:04:54,520
for investigation.

101
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,400
Well...

102
00:05:02,880 --> 00:05:03,720
What's wrong?

103
00:05:05,820 --> 00:05:06,950
What does that mean?

104
00:05:07,660 --> 00:05:09,180
I think Liang is having a meeting,

105
00:05:09,180 --> 00:05:10,280
so he missed your call.

106
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:11,880
At this point,

107
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:13,440
I don't think he has time...

108
00:05:13,860 --> 00:05:15,400
His phone is off.

109
00:05:15,800 --> 00:05:17,000
He can't answer any calls.

110
00:05:17,730 --> 00:05:19,080
Just tell me what happened.

111
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:21,750
Hurry. Otherwise, I'll ask the police.

112
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,770
What are you waiting for?

113
00:05:22,770 --> 00:05:23,920
Just tell us what happened.

114
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:29,400
I think Liang is also
under investigation.

115
00:05:32,880 --> 00:05:33,720
Investigation?

116
00:05:34,350 --> 00:05:35,440
Is it related to Bao's case?

117
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:36,830
I'm not sure.

118
00:05:37,320 --> 00:05:39,020
Sister, don't worry.

119
00:05:39,020 --> 00:05:40,700
I'll figure it out.

120
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:43,720
I can't believe it.

121
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,840
They have a plan.

122
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,600
They're starting to take people down.

123
00:05:52,020 --> 00:05:53,440
If Liang was fine,

124
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:55,000
Bao might be in danger.

125
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,520
But Liang was taken away,

126
00:05:57,410 --> 00:05:58,880
so Bao will be fine.

127
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,650
Your logic is correct,

128
00:06:01,250 --> 00:06:02,640
and they understand it too.

129
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,480
But I'm still worried.

130
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:08,080
Well, what if...

131
00:06:08,810 --> 00:06:09,880
Just in case.

132
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:12,030
If Bao is really guilty,

133
00:06:12,030 --> 00:06:13,760
Liang won't get away with it.

134
00:06:13,850 --> 00:06:14,690
Bao...

135
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,150
No matter what,

136
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:17,600
their ultimate goal

137
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:18,670
must be Tuan Island.

138
00:06:19,890 --> 00:06:21,900
If the accusation against Bao is true,

139
00:06:21,900 --> 00:06:23,220
Dian Lao'er's shares

140
00:06:23,230 --> 00:06:24,480
will become the focus again,

141
00:06:24,650 --> 00:06:25,680
and Qi Hanchen

142
00:06:25,840 --> 00:06:27,000
will benefit from it.

143
00:06:29,410 --> 00:06:31,500
- Can you get in touch with Haicheng?
- Yes.

144
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:33,840
But I think

145
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:36,280
they'll ask for much at this point.

146
00:06:38,080 --> 00:06:39,030
They only want money,

147
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:41,360
but Qi Hanchen wants our lives.

148
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,320
Okay, I'll call them.

149
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:46,680
By the way,

150
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:50,240
Qi Hanchen has planned this
for a long time.

151
00:06:50,960 --> 00:06:52,120
He'll spread bad rumors

152
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,540
about Tuan Island.

153
00:06:54,320 --> 00:06:55,160
I've been there.

154
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:56,120
Leave it to me.

155
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:58,000
You have more important things to do.

156
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,880
We don't have time.

157
00:07:00,890 --> 00:07:02,000
We need to split up.

158
00:07:07,220 --> 00:07:09,460
(MorningStar Group)

159
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:10,840
A report can also

160
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:12,000
make a difference.

161
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,360
As a unit chief,

162
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,840
he can't be completely innocent.

163
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,580
According to our source,

164
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,040
apart from the report letter,

165
00:07:21,330 --> 00:07:22,180
there's another reason

166
00:07:22,180 --> 00:07:23,200
why he's being investigated.

167
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,400
The shooter

168
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:27,000
accused Bao Chenyan of hiring a killer.

169
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,080
Xing Liang knew it

170
00:07:29,280 --> 00:07:30,160
but released him.

171
00:07:30,440 --> 00:07:31,600
He violated regulations.

172
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,560
Hiring a killer?

173
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:36,760
Who arranged it?

174
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:56,880
Uncle Long.

175
00:07:57,960 --> 00:08:00,440
Bao Chenyan was accused of
hiring a killer.

176
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:02,920
Did your friend do it?

177
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:05,360
It's the skill of tightening the net.

178
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:08,680
I'm so impressed.

179
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:10,920
I'd like to invite your friend

180
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,620
to Guanhai Tea House

181
00:08:13,350 --> 00:08:16,280
to exchange fishing tips in two days.

182
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,240
Is he available?

183
00:08:19,390 --> 00:08:21,160
Okay, I'll tell him.

184
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:32,780
This man is very greedy.

185
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:35,280
It's not just Tuan Island.

186
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:39,040
In my opinion,

187
00:08:39,670 --> 00:08:41,140
he not only wants to

188
00:08:41,140 --> 00:08:42,500
get rid of Bao Chenyan for good

189
00:08:44,890 --> 00:08:46,600
but also wants to set up Xing Liang.

190
00:08:48,100 --> 00:08:49,320
He's cunning

191
00:08:50,860 --> 00:08:52,080
and cruel.

192
00:08:54,680 --> 00:08:55,700
We must be careful

193
00:08:55,700 --> 00:08:57,240
when dealing with him.

194
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:59,040
Mr. Qi,

195
00:08:59,670 --> 00:09:00,920
is it too dangerous for you

196
00:09:01,460 --> 00:09:02,580
to meet with someone like him?

197
00:09:05,760 --> 00:09:07,080
I'm doing this because

198
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:09,120
I want to know what he's got.

199
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:11,640
Like I said,

200
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:13,680
the enemy of my enemy is my friend.

201
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:15,840
He's dealing with

202
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:17,480
Bao Chenyan and Xing Liang,

203
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,160
and it's good

204
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:20,440
for us.

205
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:22,680
Talk to Mr. Wang

206
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,160
and apply for

207
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:25,640
an administrative review.

208
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:26,880
Just tell them

209
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,040
Bao Chenyan is suspected of
hiring a killer

210
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,960
and unjust enrichment.

211
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:32,480
Okay.

212
00:09:41,700 --> 00:09:43,380
(Binjiang Criminal Police Unit)

213
00:09:58,170 --> 00:09:59,010
Where are you going?

214
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,520
Can't you just stop?

215
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:03,320
Binbin, listen.

216
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:04,600
Stop asking.

217
00:10:05,140 --> 00:10:06,410
You got me wrong.

218
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:08,040
My sister wanted to know.

219
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,520
Do you want to deal with her?

220
00:10:15,880 --> 00:10:17,360
Fine, I'm leaving.

221
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:18,620
I'll send her the address

222
00:10:18,620 --> 00:10:19,480
and let her come.

223
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:22,080
Stop.

224
00:10:24,280 --> 00:10:25,680
If I knew you'd wait for me,

225
00:10:26,710 --> 00:10:28,360
I'd rather stay at the DIC.

226
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:30,840
Listen,

227
00:10:31,040 --> 00:10:32,400
why is Bao Chenyan's murder accusation

228
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,060
related to Xing Liang?

229
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,600
Before Bao Chenyan was released,

230
00:10:42,760 --> 00:10:43,860
(Binjiang CPB)
Chen Yiming

231
00:10:43,860 --> 00:10:45,240
had made clear accusations.

232
00:10:45,860 --> 00:10:47,080
As the person in charge,

233
00:10:47,560 --> 00:10:48,520
why did you release him

234
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:50,040
before solving the case?

235
00:10:51,310 --> 00:10:52,150
Yes,

236
00:10:52,520 --> 00:10:53,360
Chen Yiming

237
00:10:53,870 --> 00:10:55,520
made accusations against Bao Chenyan.

238
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:57,000
However,

239
00:10:57,530 --> 00:10:58,920
none of them

240
00:10:59,580 --> 00:11:00,680
can be used

241
00:11:01,300 --> 00:11:03,330
as solid evidence.

242
00:11:04,040 --> 00:11:05,080
In such circumstances,

243
00:11:05,560 --> 00:11:06,520
I had no reason

244
00:11:06,790 --> 00:11:08,200
to extend Bao Chenyan's detention.

245
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:10,040
After all,

246
00:11:10,890 --> 00:11:12,360
he was arrested for fighting,

247
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,200
a security incident,

248
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:15,240
instead of a criminal case.

249
00:11:15,820 --> 00:11:17,080
After being released,

250
00:11:17,590 --> 00:11:19,120
he went to the hearing

251
00:11:19,340 --> 00:11:20,420
regarding to

252
00:11:20,950 --> 00:11:22,790
the share transfer agreement
between Wen Group

253
00:11:23,040 --> 00:11:24,000
and Benniu Group.

254
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,280
As far as we know,

255
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:28,120
the actual controller
of Wen's Tuan Island Trading Co., Ltd.

256
00:11:28,410 --> 00:11:29,280
is Bao Chenyan,

257
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:30,640
and your wife

258
00:11:30,760 --> 00:11:31,600
Wen Zixuan

259
00:11:31,800 --> 00:11:33,590
is the investor.

260
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:35,880
Did you release Bao Chenyan

261
00:11:36,040 --> 00:11:37,160
at this point

262
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,600
to protect Tuan Island Trading's

263
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:40,220
business interest?

264
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:43,920
No.

265
00:11:45,110 --> 00:11:46,660
If he'd done it before,

266
00:11:46,660 --> 00:11:48,550
my sister would've been a billionaire.

267
00:11:48,550 --> 00:11:49,880
Why would she work so hard?

268
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:52,280
At this critical moment,

269
00:11:52,930 --> 00:11:54,240
no one cares about the process

270
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:55,680
but the result.

271
00:11:56,800 --> 00:11:58,720
They set us up

272
00:11:59,880 --> 00:12:01,320
for Tuan Island.

273
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:03,760
They want to get all of us
into this mess.

274
00:12:04,760 --> 00:12:06,200
It's not just a trap.

275
00:12:07,640 --> 00:12:09,120
They want to take care of

276
00:12:09,680 --> 00:12:11,000
Mr. Xing for good.

277
00:12:13,560 --> 00:12:14,400
What do you mean?

278
00:12:15,040 --> 00:12:16,280
Do you know Li Xiangyuan?

279
00:12:18,470 --> 00:12:19,370
Yes.

280
00:12:19,370 --> 00:12:20,300
What's your relationship?

281
00:12:20,580 --> 00:12:22,020
We were classmates in middle school.

282
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:23,690
Did you help him solve

283
00:12:23,690 --> 00:12:24,740
a public security issue?

284
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:27,840
Yes.

285
00:12:28,760 --> 00:12:29,800
It was

286
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:31,720
a labor dispute.

287
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:33,200
Some people

288
00:12:33,550 --> 00:12:34,830
broke into their company

289
00:12:34,830 --> 00:12:35,840
and smashed their office.

290
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:37,160
He called the police.

291
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:39,240
However,

292
00:12:39,580 --> 00:12:40,660
this case was taken over

293
00:12:40,660 --> 00:12:41,900
by the police station

294
00:12:41,900 --> 00:12:42,830
